S.FORM: == kakiliman == Ci-cya-li 吉佳利 Ci-cya-li "Lu-an-ta a kamu, Kigali,(ci.ɡɑ́.ɾi))nu Lu-an-ta a angangan nu tukay atu satabakiay a tukuy, zuma kitizaan a lala' macapi tu kaecapuan nuyni a kanatal. makay 1962 a mihcaan uyni sateked nu Lu-an-ta, Ci-cya-li nu Lu-an-ta a cen-ce, keyzay atu lalangawan a kasaupu, imahini uyza angangan nuyni a saculilan nu kanatal. mala angangan nuyni a kanatal, 吉佳利(盧安達語:Kigali,(ci.ɡɑ́.ɾi)) , nilaculan Ci-cya-li u Cong-tung nu Lu-an-ta atu zuma a cung-ng cen-bu a pikawawan atu sakakaay akitizaan. Ci-cya-li a tukay itini i labu a kuwan nu Ci-cya-li, 2006 a mihca 1 a bulad hamin mikawaway misumad tu sakuwan a tukay misatabaki tu liwliw nu Ci-cya-li katukuh hamin hekal nu sakuwan nu Ci-cya-li. hamin nu hekal 730 pin-bang kung-li, zuma nu tukayay a kakitizaan macalap ku 70%. 70%. likisi 歷史 ayw nu 8000 a mihcaan katukuh tu 3000 a mihcaan, Te-wa a binacadan nu ayzaay a Lu-an-ta. Te-wa a binacadan nu Pi-ke-mi a tademawan, uyni a tademawan itawya u miadupay u ala ku nikauzip. ayaw nu 700 a mihcaan katukuh 1500 a mihcaan, pasu ayzaay a Bu-tu a binacadan atu pasu Tu-si a binacadanay a Pan-tu a tademaw malingatu i ayzay a Lu-an-ta tiza manaeng katuh ayza. namalingatu katukuh ayza, Pan-tu micumud tu tu malukay a tukay, uyaanay a kilakilangan maletek mapatades mala sakalukan a lala'. Ci-cya-li u kasaupuan nu keyzey ku Lu-an-ta, Lu-an-ta a labu nu kanatal u satabakiay a tukuy nu misiwbayay. angangan a nilatul sa u midapay a kawaw, kitakit a gingku u piasip tu midapay a kawaw macalap tu 2014 a mihcaan GDP a 53%. satabakiay u mangelu'ay a kawaw u nisalunguc nilacul nikalukan nibutingan atu kilang a kawaw, u calap tu mangeluay a kawaw 24%, 2012 a mihcaan pulung a niasipan, sakaluk a lala' u calap tu tukay a ahebal ikaka tu 60%. 2014年GDP的53%. 60%以上. 2014 a mihcaan, Ci-cya-li a kusian a ngangayaw pasu miculu'ay tu zaylyaw patayza labu nu kanatal talakaw ku nipalawpes tu kalisiw, saaca azaaw ku nisanga'an atu nayi' ku tatanengan tu tademaw. Ci-cya-li micapi tu Si-s a piba'tuan a kitizaan, Si-s taneng misanga' tu si atu cin. mipatadas tu si atu cin tini i saamisan nu cacay a bataan a kung-li nu Rutongo, mipatadas tu si itini Nyakabingo, laed tu Ci-cya-li pakala tu cacay a bataan a kung-li. yadah ku ba'tu a kakelul han patahkal patayzi i zumaan a kanatal amisanga' mimelmel, nika itawya iza ku kapahay a kikay tu sapimelmel tu ba'tu, pasu i Ci-cya-li tu saamisan a Ka-lu-lu-ma pisanga'an mimelmel a kusi, i 1980 a ziday patizeng, 2019 a mihcaan tu nisulitan taneng izaw ku 1,800 kung-tun "1,800, ku tanayu' kung-tu, 2000 ku apuyu' kung-tun" ku tatenga'ay a si. duduc Lu-an-ta 2012 a mihcaan tu pikingsa tu tademaw, Ci-cya-li a tademaw izaw ku 1,132,686 ku tademaw, zuma 859,332 ku tademaw muenengay i tukuy a kitizaan. Ci-cya-li a tukay nu Lu-an-ta lima a sakuwan sakawawan nu kasacacay, uyza cacay aca a "tukay" u sakuwan pulung iza ku tulu a kitizaan mikawaw, pasazuma tu kitizaan nu Ka-sa-pow "Gasabo District", kitizaan nu Ci-ku-low "Kicukiro District" atu kitizaan nu Ni-ya-lu "Nyarugenge District". 2006 a m ihcaan pikawawan ayaw nu pisumad tu Ci-cya-li a niyazu' "Ci-cya-li", mamin misumad papulung pacumud labu nu Ci-cya-li. mikuwan tu saykay u nipili'an nu binawlan a sakaput mikawaway a wi-yen ku sitatungusay, mikawaway a wi-yen u kingciw atu mitayliay tu kinciw tatusa, tatulu mapulung situngus mikawaw tu seyhu. (Gasabo District),基庫基羅區(Kicukiro District)和尼亞魯岡區(Nyarugenge District).2006 (Kigali-Rural Province), . malalitin tu i hekalay atu zumaay a natinengan

== kakiliman == Ci-cya-li 吉佳利 Ci-cya-li "Lo-an-ta a kamo, Kigali,(ci.ɡɑ́.ɾi))no Lo-an-ta a angangan no tokay ato satabakiay a tokoy, zoma kitizaan a lala' macapi to kaecapoan noyni a kanatal. makay 1962 a mihcaan oyni sateked no Lo-an-ta, Ci-cya-li no Lo-an-ta a cen-ce, keyzay ato lalangawan a kasaopo, imahini oyza angangan noyni a sacolilan no kanatal. mala angangan noyni a kanatal, 吉佳利(盧安達語:Kigali,(ci.ɡɑ́.ɾi)) , nilacolan Ci-cya-li o Cong-tong no Lo-an-ta ato zoma a cong-ng cen-bo a pikawawan ato sakakaay akitizaan. Ci-cya-li a tokay itini i labo a kowan no Ci-cya-li, 2006 a mihca 1 a bolad hamin mikawaway misomad to sakowan a tokay misatabaki to liwliw no Ci-cya-li katokoh hamin hekal no sakowan no Ci-cya-li. hamin no hekal 730 pin-bang kong-li, zoma no tokayay a kakitizaan macalap ko 70%. 70%. likisi 歷史 ayw no 8000 a mihcaan katokoh to 3000 a mihcaan, Te-wa a binacadan no ayzaay a Lo-an-ta. Te-wa a binacadan no Pi-ke-mi a tademawan, oyni a tademawan itawya o miadopay o ala ko nikaozip. ayaw no 700 a mihcaan katokoh 1500 a mihcaan, paso ayzaay a Bo-to a binacadan ato paso To-si a binacadanay a Pan-to a tademaw malingato i ayzay a Lo-an-ta tiza manaeng katoh ayza. namalingato katokoh ayza, Pan-to micomod to to malokay a tokay, oyaanay a kilakilangan maletek mapatades mala sakalokan a lala'. Ci-cya-li o kasaopoan no keyzey ko Lo-an-ta, Lo-an-ta a labo no kanatal o satabakiay a tokoy no misiwbayay. angangan a nilatol sa o midapay a kawaw, kitakit a gingko o piasip to midapay a kawaw macalap to 2014 a mihcaan GDP a 53%. satabakiay o mangelo'ay a kawaw o nisalongoc nilacol nikalokan nibotingan ato kilang a kawaw, o calap to mangeloay a kawaw 24%, 2012 a mihcaan polong a niasipan, sakalok a lala' o calap to tokay a ahebal ikaka to 60%. 2014年GDP的53%. 60%以上. 2014 a mihcaan, Ci-cya-li a kosian a ngangayaw paso micolo'ay to zaylyaw patayza labo no kanatal talakaw ko nipalawpes to kalisiw, saaca azaaw ko nisanga'an ato nayi' ko tatanengan to tademaw. Ci-cya-li micapi to Si-s a piba'toan a kitizaan, Si-s taneng misanga' to si ato cin. mipatadas to si ato cin tini i saamisan no cacay a bataan a kong-li no Rotongo, mipatadas to si itini Nyakabingo, laed to Ci-cya-li pakala to cacay a bataan a kong-li. yadah ko ba'to a kakelol han patahkal patayzi i zomaan a kanatal amisanga' mimelmel, nika itawya iza ko kapahay a kikay to sapimelmel to ba'to, paso i Ci-cya-li to saamisan a Ka-lo-lo-ma pisanga'an mimelmel a kosi, i 1980 a ziday patizeng, 2019 a mihcaan to nisolitan taneng izaw ko 1,800 kong-ton "1,800, ko tanayo' kong-to, 2000 ko apoyo' kong-ton" ko tatenga'ay a si. dodoc Lo-an-ta 2012 a mihcaan to pikingsa to tademaw, Ci-cya-li a tademaw izaw ko 1,132,686 ko tademaw, zoma 859,332 ko tademaw moenengay i tokoy a kitizaan. Ci-cya-li a tokay no Lo-an-ta lima a sakowan sakawawan no kasacacay, oyza cacay aca a "tokay" o sakowan polong iza ko tolo a kitizaan mikawaw, pasazoma to kitizaan no Ka-sa-pow "Gasabo District", kitizaan no Ci-ko-low "Kicokiro District" ato kitizaan no Ni-ya-lo "Nyarogenge District". 2006 a m ihcaan pikawawan ayaw no pisomad to Ci-cya-li a niyazo' "Ci-cya-li", mamin misomad papolong pacomod labo no Ci-cya-li. mikowan to saykay o nipili'an no binawlan a sakapot mikawaway a wi-yen ko sitatongosay, mikawaway a wi-yen o kingciw ato mitayliay to kinciw tatosa, tatolo mapolong sitongos mikawaw to seyho.
